thread.title: BRIEF-MRM FY Gross Rental Income Down At ‍​11.2 Million Euros

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-MRM FY Gross Rental Income Down At ‍​11.2 Million Euros
text:
Feb 23 (Reuters) - MRM SA:
* FY GROSS RENTAL INCOME EUR ‍​11.2 MILLION VERSUS EUR 13.0 MILLION YEAR AGO
* PROPOSES DISTRIBUTION OF EUR 0.11 PER SHARE * FY PORTFOLIO VALUE 199.6 MILLION EUR VERSUS 197.8 MILLION EUR YEAR AGO
* OCCUPANCY RATE FOR RETAIL PORTFOLIO AT END FY ‍​ 76 PERCENT VERSUS 84 PERCENT YEAR AGO
* FY NET TRIPLE EPRA NAV AT 118.0 MILLION EUR Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
